1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,509
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,979
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,159
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,399
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,729
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,319
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,609
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,059
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,289
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,709
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,199
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,749
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,169
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,999
=No Way! My Bro is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 7=

19
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:16,990
Wait!

20
00:01:21,670 --> 00:01:25,070
You are both great warriors of Jing.

21
00:01:25,530 --> 00:01:29,550
I believe this duel should go no further
than testing each other's skills.

22
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:31,559
Fists have no eyes.

23
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,629
A duel isn't meant to be restrained.

24
00:01:33,630 --> 00:01:37,680
Your Majesty, let us begin.

25
00:01:38,630 --> 00:01:39,950
Easy now.

26
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:42,760
Jing values martial prowess.

27
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:48,709
Having both General Gu and General Sun

28
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:50,200
is my great fortune.

29
00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:52,480
A toast to you both.

30
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:03,839
We've had the liquor.

31
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,069
Are we fighting or not?

32
00:02:05,070 --> 00:02:07,840
Your Majesty, are you stalling

33
00:02:07,990 --> 00:02:10,160
because you're favoring General Gu?

34
00:02:20,700 --> 00:02:22,470
Kidnapping the imperial consort

35
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,800
is punishable
by exterminating nine clans.

36
00:02:25,990 --> 00:02:28,590
Once I become the prince consort,

37
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:31,880
Consort Nan will return to the palace
safe and sound.

38
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,110
If I win,

39
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,160
she dies.

40
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:45,420
If I lose,

41
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:48,830
Xiao Ling is mine.

42
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:52,880
Make your choice now.

43
00:02:57,790 --> 00:02:59,110
You win.

44
00:03:04,630 --> 00:03:05,750
I surrender.

45
00:03:18,070 --> 00:03:19,830
General Sun wins.

46
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,680
Bravo!

47
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:46,640
Your Majesty, please eat something.

48
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,590
You haven't eaten all day.

49
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,270
Leave us.

50
00:03:51,230 --> 00:03:52,549
Guard the door.

51
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:53,999
Let no one come near.

52
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,110
Yes, Your Majesty.

53
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,919
Sun Beiming has some nerve.

54
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,990
He dared kidnap an imperial consort.

55
00:04:03,830 --> 00:04:05,520
Now he's shown his true colors.

56
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,629
He wants my throne,

57
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:10,200
bullies my friend,

58
00:04:10,370 --> 00:04:11,589
kidnaps my consort,

59
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:13,480
and now he wants to marry you.

60
00:04:14,790 --> 00:04:16,390
I'm going to kill

61
00:04:16,670 --> 00:04:18,520
Sun Beiming.

62
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:23,800
There's another way out of this.

63
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,920
You

64
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:27,320
marry Sun Beiming.

65
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,990
Gu Bei!

66
00:04:29,350 --> 00:04:31,830
You actually tell me
to marry that traitor?

67
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,159
Have you lost your mind?

68
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,080
Gu Bei,

69
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:35,990
Xiao Ling is my sister.

70
00:04:36,110 --> 00:04:37,159
You only care about yours.

71
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,430
What about mine?

72
00:04:44,950 --> 00:04:46,549
Aren't we trying to think of a way?

73
00:04:46,550 --> 00:04:47,870
What other choice do we have?

74
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:50,150
Gu Nan is in their hands.

75
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:52,040
How can you be sure she is safe?

76
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:53,920
Answer me.

77
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,520
Answer!

78
00:04:58,390 --> 00:04:59,310
Gu Bei.

79
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:02,150
I truly admired you.

80
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:03,640
I liked you.

81
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:05,360
Turns out

82
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:07,439
I was wrong about you

83
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:09,270
all along.

84
00:05:14,450 --> 00:05:17,080
(Honor Learning and Confucianism)
Here's the gift registry I prepared.

85
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,600
(Wedding Gift Registry)
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

86
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,029
I won't neglect

87
00:05:20,030 --> 00:05:21,640
Her Highness.

88
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:27,920
Where is Consort Nan?

89
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:33,039
Her disappearance

90
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,070
concerns me as well.

91
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:36,510
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

92
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:39,689
I've ordered the Imperial Guards
to seal off the capital.

93
00:05:39,690 --> 00:05:43,840
I'm sure Consort Nan
will be found soon.

94
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:47,750
Here's a map of Jing.

95
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:50,109
Bring Consort Nan back safely,

96
00:05:50,110 --> 00:05:51,749
give up marrying the princess,

97
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:52,670
and I

98
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:55,600
will grant you a fiefdom.

99
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:57,840
You're free to choose your own territory.

100
00:05:58,530 --> 00:06:00,600
Your Majesty,
what is this supposed to mean?

101
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:04,079
I won the duel.

102
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:06,100
I should be the prince consort.

103
00:06:06,110 --> 00:06:09,719
Besides, I've admired
Princess Xiao Ling for years.

104
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:13,330
I've already prepared
the betrothal gifts.

105
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,800
You admired me?

106
00:06:20,670 --> 00:06:21,800
Xiao Ling.

107
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,800
I'll marry you.

108
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,789
Xiao Ling.

109
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:28,430
Your Majesty, my marriage is my choice.

110
00:06:28,990 --> 00:06:30,280
Besides,

111
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:32,630
General Sun is a great warrior.

112
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:34,510
What more could I ask for

113
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,430
than a husband like him?

114
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,160
I'm not finished.

115
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,800
I'll marry you,

116
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,550
but on one condition.

117
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:44,360
Please name it, Your Highness.

118
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:45,869
On our wedding day,

119
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:48,109
I won't marry into
your general's residence.

120
00:06:48,110 --> 00:06:51,670
The banquet and wedding night
must be held at my palace.

121
00:06:53,110 --> 00:06:54,870
Enough. Step back.

122
00:06:56,350 --> 00:06:59,280
As Your Highness wishes.

123
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,750
And one more thing.

124
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:03,400
After the wedding,

125
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:06,280
I must see Consort Nan
return safely to the palace.

126
00:07:06,350 --> 00:07:10,479
I'll do everything I can

127
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,040
to bring Consort Nan back.

128
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,580
Well done.

129
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,460
You're finally

130
00:07:25,890 --> 00:07:27,550
one step closer

131
00:07:27,810 --> 00:07:29,310
to marrying Xiao Ling.

132
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:32,109
For tomorrow's wedding,

133
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:34,589
I've prepared a special gift.

134
00:07:34,590 --> 00:07:37,950
It'll ensure everything goes smoothly.

135
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:40,550
As you command.

136
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:43,120
(Happiness)

137
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:53,160
Your Highness,

138
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,750
it's lively outside.

139
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:59,800
Why not join my men for a few drinks?

140
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:08,720
Quite the proud royal princess,
aren't you?

141
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:12,240
Let me make one thing clear.

142
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,719
Once you marry into the Sun family,

143
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,870
alive,

144
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,949
you're one of us.

145
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,270
Dead,

146
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,720
you still belong to us.

147
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:24,570
If you dare defy me,

148
00:08:24,990 --> 00:08:27,720
I'll make you wish you were dead.

149
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,640
Look.

150
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:38,480
The whole capital is celebrating
my wedding.

151
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:57,820
General Sun and the Princess
must be enjoying their wedding night.

152
00:08:58,280 --> 00:09:00,300
Lucky them.

153
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:05,839
Too bad we didn't get
to attend the feast.

154
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,410
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

155
00:09:23,990 --> 00:09:25,070
Why are you here?

156
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,240
My dear,

157
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,110
how do I look?

158
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:32,439
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

159
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,819
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

160
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:40,259
♪The brainy emperor
plots the strategy♪

161
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:44,639
♪The slacker general
leads the charge♪

162
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:47,049
♪Swords clash and
warhorses thunder♪

163
00:09:47,050 --> 00:09:49,589
♪Let the history
judge our deeds♪

164
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:55,259
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

165
00:09:55,260 --> 00:10:00,820
♪Peace across the
land, carefree at last♪

166
00:10:05,110 --> 00:10:07,170
♪Funny moments never stop♪

167
00:10:07,790 --> 00:10:09,980
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

168
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:14,349
♪Yet through every up and down♪

169
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:16,320
♪We create miracles♪

170
00:10:16,620 --> 00:10:19,080
♪From naive youths♪

171
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:21,819
♪To legendary heroes♪

172
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:23,769
♪This journey♪

173
00:10:23,770 --> 00:10:27,779
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

174
00:10:27,780 --> 00:10:30,330
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

175
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:35,670
♪Let's create♪

176
00:10:37,710 --> 00:10:45,630
♪A legend of our own♪

